            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Open any video, hit \"Auto Captions,\" select your language, and wait. CapCut's speech recognition is shockingly accurate—I'd say 95%+ on clear audio. After it finishes, you can tweak individual words, adjust timing, and style the text with one click.",
